
units         metal
dimension     3
atom_style    molecular
atom_modify   map array
boundary      p p p
pair_style    eam/fs
read_data     tmp0.dat
pair_coeff    *  *  Fe-P.eam.fs  Fe P
neighbor 2.0 bin
neigh_modify every 1 delay 0 check yes
timestep    0.002000
compute     pe  all pe
compute     ke  all ke


group      gfixed id < 5

fix 1 gfixed setforce 0.0 0.0 0.0
minimize     0.0 1.0e-6 1000   10000
unfix 1
run 0
write_data  Runner_0/tmp1.dat